name: 15+ Minutes of Afternoon Heavy Action at YYC Calgary International Airport!
description:
Back in April, when VivaAerobus still had their seasonal service, I headed out to YYC to film their final arrival and departure, and also filmed some of our typical afternoon heavy lineup! Includes KLM, Hainan, and our usual Canadian heavies from AC and WestJet! Hope you enjoy this compilation.

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

FLIGHT INFO
#1: Hainan Airlines A330-200 - "Hainan 7977 heavy" - PEK-YYC
#2: KLM A330-300 - "KLM 677 heavy" - AMS-YYC
#3: Air Canada B767-300ER - "Air Canada 010 heavy" - YYC-YYZ
#4: Air Canada B767-300ER - "Air Canada 009 heavy" - YYC-NRT
#5: Air Canada B787-9 - "Air Canada 851 heavy" - LHR-YYC
#6: WestJet B767-300ER - "WestJet 2 heavy" - LGW-YYC
#7: KLM A330-300  - "KLM 678 heavy" - YYC-AMS 
#7: Hainan Airlines A330-200  - "Hainan 7978 heavy" - YYC-PEK
